    "developed a deep learning-based cartilage lesion model, with a high diagnostic performance and good intraobserver agreement for detecting cartilage degeneration and acute cartilage injury [20].",
    "developed a deep learning algorithm to detect rotator cuff tear with 87% accuracy [49].",
    "Hong et al.",
    "developed an AI model to analyze the efficacy of knee ligament trauma repair [50].Ultrasound-based AI algorithms have been only mildly investigated compared to other imaging modalities.",
